<h3 id="instale-o-java-jdk-e-configure-o-java_home">Instale o Java JDK e configure o JAVA_HOME</h3>

<p>Instale o Java 8 com o seguinte comando:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">~# apt-get <span class="nb">install </span>openjdk-8-jdk</code></pre></figure>

<p>Verifique a instala√ß√£o do Java:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">~# java <span class="nt">-version</span></code></pre></figure>

<p>Adicionar o JAVA_HOME na vari√°vel PATH:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">~# vim /etc/environments</code></pre></figure>

<p>Adicionar ao final do arquivo a vari√°vel JAVA_HOME:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">~# <span class="nv">JAVA_HOME</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">"/usr/lib/jvm/java-8-openjdk-amd64"</span></code></pre></figure>

<p>Atualize os √≠ndices da vari√°vel de ambiente:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">~# <span class="nb">source</span> /etc/environment</code></pre></figure>

<p>Verifique se o Path est√° correto:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">~# <span class="nb">echo</span> <span class="nv">$JAVA_HOME</span></code></pre></figure>

<h3 id="instale-e-configure-o-servidor-ssh-sem-senha">Instale e Configure o Servidor SSH (Sem Senha)</h3>

<p>Caso n√£o tenha instalado o ssh, instale o servidor ssh com o seguinte comando:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">~# apt-get <span class="nb">install </span>ssh</code></pre></figure>

<p>Verifique se a m√°quina tem acesso a ssh sem senha no localhost:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">~# ssh localhost</code></pre></figure>

<p>Caso seja solicitado uma senha, fa√ßa o seguinte procedimento:</p>

<p>Gere uma chave p√∫blica de acesso ao ssh</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">~# ssh-keygen <span class="nt">-t</span> rsa <span class="nt">-P</span> <span class="s2">""</span></code></pre></figure>

<p>Agora com a chave gerada e adicione ela ao diret√≥rio de chaves autorizadas:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">~# <span class="nb">cat</span> <span class="nv">$HOME</span>/.ssh/id_rsa.pub <span class="o">&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="nv">$HOME</span>/.ssh/authorized_keys</code></pre></figure>

<h3 id="configure-o-apache-hadoop-single-node">Configure o Apache Hadoop (Single Node)</h3>

<p>Fa√ßa o download do Apache Hadoop, neste caso a vers√£o 2.8.1:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">~# wget http://mirror.nbtelecom.com.br/apache/hadoop/common/hadoop-2.8.1/hadoop-2.8.1.tar.gz</code></pre></figure>

<p>Descompacte o Apache Hadoop no diret√≥rio /opt:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">~# <span class="nb">tar</span> <span class="nt">-zxvf</span> hadoop-2.8.1.tar.gz</code></pre></figure>

<p>Agora configure as vari√°veis de ambiente:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell"><span class="c">#caso voc√™ prefira que todos usu√°rios do sistema tenham as vari√°veis de ambiente</span>
~# vim /etc/profile </code></pre></figure>

<p>ou</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell"><span class="c">#caso voc√™ prefira que apenas o seu usu√°rio tenham as vari√°veis de ambiente</span>
~# vim ~/.bashrc </code></pre></figure>

<p>Adicione ao final do arquivo os seguintes vari√°veis de ambiente:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell"><span class="c">#HADOOP VARIABLES START</span>
<span class="nb">export </span><span class="nv">JAVA_HOME</span><span class="o">=</span>caminho_para_o_java_home
<span class="nb">export </span><span class="nv">HADOOP_INSTALL</span><span class="o">=</span>caminho_para_o_haddop
<span class="nb">export </span><span class="nv">PATH</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="nv">$PATH</span>:<span class="nv">$HADOOP_INSTALL</span>/bin
<span class="nb">export </span><span class="nv">PATH</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="nv">$PATH</span>:<span class="nv">$HADOOP_INSTALL</span>/sbin
<span class="nb">export </span><span class="nv">HADOOP_MAPRED_HOME</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="nv">$HADOOP_INSTALL</span>
<span class="nb">export </span><span class="nv">HADOOP_COMMON_HOME</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="nv">$HADOOP_INSTALL</span>
<span class="nb">export </span><span class="nv">HADOOP_HDFS_HOME</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="nv">$HADOOP_INSTALL</span>
<span class="nb">export </span><span class="nv">YARN_HOME</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="nv">$HADOOP_INSTALL</span>
<span class="nb">export </span><span class="nv">HADOOP_COMMON_LIB_NATIVE_DIR</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="nv">$HADOOP_INSTALL</span>/lib/native
<span class="nb">export </span><span class="nv">HADOOP_OPTS</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">"-Djava.library.path=</span><span class="nv">$HADOOP_INSTALL</span><span class="s2">/lib"</span>
<span class="c">#HADOOP VARIABLES END</span></code></pre></figure>

<p>OBS: Substitua <strong><em>caminho_para_o_java_home</em></strong> e <strong><em>caminho_para_o_hadoop</em></strong> pelos seus respectivos paths ;)</p>

<p>Atualize os √≠ndices das vari√°veis de ambiente:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">~# <span class="nb">source</span> ~/.bashrc</code></pre></figure>

<p>ou</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">~# <span class="nb">source</span> /etc/profile</code></pre></figure>

<p>Agora edite o arquivo de vari√°veis de ambiente do Hadoop:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">~# vim hadoop-2.8.1/etc/hadoop/hadoop-env.sh</code></pre></figure>

<p>Edite a vari√°vel de ambiente JAVA_HOME:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">~# <span class="nb">export </span><span class="nv">JAVA_HOME</span><span class="o">=</span>/usr/lib/jvm/java-8-openjdk-amd64</code></pre></figure>

<p>Crie o diret√≥rio onde ser√° o ponto de montagem do sistemas de arquivos do Hadoop o HDFS:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">~# <span class="nb">mkdir</span> <span class="nt">-p</span> ~/hadoop_store/hdfs/namenode
~# <span class="nb">mkdir</span> <span class="nt">-p</span> ~/hadoop_store/hdfs/datanode</code></pre></figure>

<p>Configure o arquivo hdfs-site.xml com o caminho das pastas criadas:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">~# vim hadoop-2.8.1/etc/hadoop/hdfs-site.xml</code></pre></figure>

<p>Adicione as seguintes propriedades:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-xml" data-lang="xml"><span class="nt">&lt;property&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;name&gt;</span>dfs.replication<span class="nt">&lt;/name&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;value&gt;</span>1<span class="nt">&lt;/value&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;description&gt;</span>Default block replication.
  The actual number of replications can be specified when the file is created.
  The default is used if replication is not specified in create time.
  <span class="nt">&lt;/description&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;/property&gt;</span>

<span class="nt">&lt;property&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;name&gt;</span>dfs.namenode.name.dir<span class="nt">&lt;/name&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;value&gt;</span>file:######NAMENODE_FOLDER_PATH######<span class="nt">&lt;/value&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;/property&gt;</span>

<span class="nt">&lt;property&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;name&gt;</span>dfs.datanode.data.dir<span class="nt">&lt;/name&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;value&gt;</span>file:######DATANODE_FOLDER_PATH######<span class="nt">&lt;/value&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;/property&gt;</span></code></pre></figure>

<p>*ps: a tag <code class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><span class="nt">&lt;/property&gt;</span></code> deve ficar dentro de uma tag <code class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><span class="nt">&lt;configuration&gt;&lt;/configuration&gt;</span></code></p>

<p>Crie um diret√≥rio tempor√°rio na pasta de instala√ß√£o do Hadoop:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">~# <span class="nb">mkdir</span> <span class="nt">-p</span> ~/hadoop_store/hdfs/tmp</code></pre></figure>

<p>Configure o arquivo core-site.xml</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">~# vim hadoop-2.8.1/etc/hadoop/core-site.xml</code></pre></figure>

<p>Adicione as seguintes propriedades</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-xml" data-lang="xml"><span class="nt">&lt;property&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;name&gt;</span>hadoop.tmp.dir<span class="nt">&lt;/name&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;value&gt;</span>######TMP_FOLDER_PATH######<span class="nt">&lt;/value&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;description&gt;</span>A base for other temporary directories.<span class="nt">&lt;/description&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;/property&gt;</span>

<span class="nt">&lt;property&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;name&gt;</span>fs.default.name<span class="nt">&lt;/name&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;value&gt;</span>hdfs://localhost:54310<span class="nt">&lt;/value&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;description&gt;</span>The name of the default file system.  A URI whose
  scheme and authority determine the FileSystem implementation.  The
  uri's scheme determines the config property (fs.SCHEME.impl) naming
  the FileSystem implementation class.  The uri's authority is used to
  determine the host, port, etc. for a filesystem.<span class="nt">&lt;/description&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;/property&gt;</span></code></pre></figure>

<p>*ps: a tag <code class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><span class="nt">&lt;/property&gt;</span></code> deve ficar dentro de uma tag <code class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><span class="nt">&lt;configuration&gt;&lt;/configuration&gt;</span></code></p>

<p>Configure o arquivo mapred-site.xml:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">~# <span class="nb">cp </span>hadoop-2.8.1/etc/hadoop/mapred-site.xml.template hadoop-2.8.1/etc/hadoop/mapred-site.xml</code></pre></figure>

<p>Adicione a seguinte propriedade:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-xml" data-lang="xml"><span class="nt">&lt;property&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;name&gt;</span>mapred.job.tracker<span class="nt">&lt;/name&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;value&gt;</span>localhost:54311<span class="nt">&lt;/value&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;description&gt;</span>The host and port that the MapReduce job tracker runs
  at.  If "local", then jobs are run in-process as a single map
  and reduce task.
  <span class="nt">&lt;/description&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;/property&gt;</span></code></pre></figure>

<p>*ps: a tag <code class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><span class="nt">&lt;/property&gt;</span></code> deve ficar dentro de uma tag <code class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><span class="nt">&lt;configuration&gt;&lt;/configuration&gt;</span></code></p>

<p>Configure o arquivo o arquivo yarn-site.xml:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">~# vim yarn-site.xml</code></pre></figure>

<p>Adicione as seguintes propriedades:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-xml" data-lang="xml"><span class="nt">&lt;property&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;name&gt;</span>yarn.resourcemanager.hostname<span class="nt">&lt;/name&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;value&gt;</span>frontend<span class="nt">&lt;/value&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;description&gt;</span>The hostname of the RM.<span class="nt">&lt;/description&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;/property&gt;</span>

<span class="nt">&lt;property&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;name&gt;</span>yarn.nodemanager.aux-services<span class="nt">&lt;/name&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;value&gt;</span>mapreduce_shuffle<span class="nt">&lt;/value&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;/property&gt;</span>

<span class="nt">&lt;property&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;name&gt;</span>yarn.nodemanager.aux-services.mapreduce.shuffle.class<span class="nt">&lt;/name&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;value&gt;</span>org.apache.hadoop.mapred.ShuffleHandler<span class="nt">&lt;/value&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;/property&gt;</span></code></pre></figure>

<p>*ps: a tag <code class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><span class="nt">&lt;/property&gt;</span></code> deve ficar dentro de uma tag <code class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><span class="nt">&lt;configuration&gt;&lt;/configuration&gt;</span></code></p>

<p>Formate o sistema de arquivos HDFS:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">~# hadoop namenode <span class="nt">-format</span></code></pre></figure>

<p>Inicie os servi√ßos do Hadoop:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">~# start-dfs.sh <span class="o">&amp;&amp;</span> start-yarn.sh</code></pre></figure>

<p>Verifique os processos do Hadoop:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">~# jps</code></pre></figure>

<p>O console deve aparecer uma sa√≠da semelhante a essa:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">9757 Jps
8950 DataNode
9145 SecondaryNameNode
9438 NodeManager
8799 NameNode
9311 ResourceManager</code></pre></figure>

<p><em>Importante que apare√ßa os processos <strong>*DataNode</strong></em>, <strong><em>SecondaryNameNode</em></strong>, <strong><em>NodeManager</em></strong>, <strong><em>NameNode</em></strong> e <strong><em>ResourceManager</em></strong>.</p>

<h2 id="configurar-o-memory-heap-da-jvm">Configurar o Memory Heap da JVM</h2>

<p>Caso enfrente algum problema com rela√ß√£o ao tamanho do <em>heap</em> de mem√≥ria da JVM</p>

<p>1¬™ Etapa:</p>

<p>Adicione esta linha no arquivo /etc/profile:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell"><span class="nb">export </span><span class="nv">JVM_ARGS</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">"-Xms1024m -Xmx1024m"</span></code></pre></figure>

<p>Esta mudan√ßa muda o heap de mem√≥ria do Java para 1024 mb. Por padr√£o √© 128 mb.</p>

<p>Atualize os √≠ndices do arquivo /etc/profile:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">~# <span class="nb">source</span> /etc/profile</code></pre></figure>

<p>2¬™ Etapa:</p>

<p>Adicione ou edite a seguinte vari√°vel de ambiente:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell">~# <span class="nb">export </span><span class="nv">HADOOP_CLIENT_OPTS</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">"-Xmx1024m </span><span class="nv">$HADOOP_CLIENT_OPTS</span><span class="s2">"</span></code></pre></figure>

<p>3¬™ Etapa:</p>

<p>Adicione a seguinte propriedade ao arquivo mapred-site.xml:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-xml" data-lang="xml"><span class="nt">&lt;property&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;name&gt;</span>mapred.child.java.opts<span class="nt">&lt;/name&gt;</span>
  <span class="nt">&lt;value&gt;</span>-Xmx1024m<span class="nt">&lt;/value&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;/property&gt;</span></code></pre></figure>

<p>*ps: a tag <code class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><span class="nt">&lt;/property&gt;</span></code> deve ficar dentro de uma tag <code class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><span class="nt">&lt;configuration&gt;&lt;/configuration&gt;</span></code></p>

<p>Se tudo estiver ok, pronto temos o Apache Hadoop configurado em modo <em>Single Node</em> ;)<br /></p>

